high_descs: Turn right at the wall ahead and face the counter on the left just before the cooktop.
Pick up the knife to the left of the spoon on the counter.
Turn around, hang a left at the counter and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the knife inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn left to face the silver dishwasher and the drawers under the counter.
Open the second drawer from the bottom, place the knife inside and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed knife in a drawer.

high_descs: Go past the door on your left and make a right at the wall, then turn to the counter on your left.
Pick up the butter knife, to the left of the spoon, on the counter.
Turn to your right and go to the end of the counter, then make a right and go to the sink on your left.
Place the knife in the sink, between the fork and the coffee cup, turn the water on, rinse the knife, turn the water off , and remove the knife from the sink.
Turn to your left and go to the drawers to the left of the dishwasher.
Place the knife in the third drawer down from the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife in the kitchen drawer.

high_descs: Go forward, turn right at the wall, go forward, turn left at the counter
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn around, go to the table, turn left, go to the counter, turn right, go forward, turn left at the sink
Put the knife into the sink, open the water, wait, pick up the knife
Turn right, go forward to the microwave
Open the second drawer from the bottom, put the knife in the drawer, close the drawer
anns.task_desc: Wash a knife and put it into a drawer
